======================== Multiple Switches Network ========================

Similar to VLANs, Multiple Switches in a network all have their own MAC Address Table
   - Switches perform switch actions independently
       - If one switch knows where to go it won't FLOOD
       - If one switch doesn't know it will FLOOD
       - Again, these actions are independent from another

